The Vehicle to Freedom

http://www.empowernetwork.com/jomo22/blog/the-vehicle-to-freedom/

Here’s a question that you might not get asked often…

What do you desire to Be, Do and Have in this lifetime?

The truth is that before you can move towards that ‘destination’, you’ve gotta make sure you are equipped with a ‘vehicle’ to get you there…

A question that will give you an EVEN DEEPER insight is this…

“Can I reach my dreams using the ‘vehicle’ that I’m currently using?”

For most people, the answer to that question is NO…

But even if the answer is YES…how long will it take you to get there?

…take a moment to HONESTLY answer that question…

Once you’ve done that, watch this video…
